title: Yu-Gi-Oh! Power of Chaos - Joey's World (MOD) (PC)
description:
Yu-Gi-Oh! Power of Chaos - Joey's World (MOD) (PC) by ristar87 (Thanks)

Opponent : Joey

Gameplay : A MOD of Joey The Passion, with twice the number of cards on the premoded version. It's a lot better than Joey The Passion, very fun to play. Enjoy Joey's cards you've never seen in gaming but only in movie!

Number of cards : 1109, all can be unlocked with the included All-Card Unlocker, if you have trouble :

Installation : Extract from the .exe on a new folder anywhere you want.

Seed & enjoy!
